project_descr: Support to the implementation of the TB and Malaria grants managed by the Ministry of Health and Child Care in Zimbabwe

outputs.output_descr: Support Services NFM Malaria seeks to reduce malaria incidence to 5/1000 and malaria deaths by at least 90% of the 2015 figure by 2020, across all the 10 provinces of Zimbabwe.
donor_name: GLOBAL FUND TO FIGHT AIDS, TUBERCULOSIS

outputs.output_descr: Support Services NFM TB seeks to reduce the TB prevalence and new infections across the 10 provinces of Zimbabwe by the year 2020.
